Package jetbrains.mps.smodel.event

Interface SModelListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SModelAdapter
    public interface SModelListener
    Author: Sergey Dmitriev Created Sep 16, 2003

    WARNING: Do not use this kind of listener in UI. In case of changes to a model that affect many nodes it might lead to performance problems. In these cases use SModelCommandListener which listens to batch notifications
